    • 方法详细资料

      • createPlantModel

        void createPlantModel(PlantModelCreationTO to)
               throws ObjectUnknownException,
                      ObjectExistsException,
                      KernelRuntimeException,
                      java.lang.IllegalStateException
        Creates a new plant model with the objects described in the given transfer object. Implicitly saves/persists the new plant model.
        参数:
        to - The transfer object describing the plant model objects to be created.
        抛出:
        ObjectUnknownException - If any referenced object does not exist.
        ObjectExistsException - If an object with the same name already exists in the model.
        KernelRuntimeException - In case there is an exception executing this method.
        java.lang.IllegalStateException - If there was a problem persisting the model.

      • getPersistentModelName

        @Deprecated
 @ScheduledApiChange(when="5.0")
java.lang.String getPersistentModelName()
                                                                              throws KernelRuntimeException,
                                                                                     java.lang.IllegalStateException
        已过时。 Fetching a persistent model's name will not be supported any more, as the model would now already be loaded, anyway.
        Returns the name of the model that is stored and could be loaded by the kernel.
        返回:
        The name of the model, or null if there is no model.
        抛出:
        KernelRuntimeException - In case there is an exception executing this method.
        java.lang.IllegalStateException - If retrieving the model name was not possible.
